amp him.  Only seen in South Ro and he is a rare spawn at that.  At least the drops are tradeable.  Next you need a LOT of coin to make this.  You have to use Platnium thread which isn't cheap.  You need a fairly high Tailoring skill.. and an item from an Enchanter.<br><br>This item says Shadow Knight more than it does Cleric.  Being Imuded by Cazic-Thule it gives more STR than the other two Erudite dieites.  Luckily it does give decent Mana.. for for a BP at the level you'd most likely be able to make this item you should have better.  Plus like I said the Necromance is left out and I see way way more Erudite Necromancers than I do Shadow Knights and Clerics combined.<br><br>Don't get me wrong I still will make this stuff.. I'd love a set if only for the Fashion, but its not practical for me to wear over what I have now.  Once I make a 2nd pair and beyond it'll most likely go to rich twinks.  </p>&nbsp;<br>Tekara Grimmhealer<br>65th Thulian Archon<br>Cazic-Thule Server</td></tr>
